sub_title: Professor at University of Amsterdam & Co-founder at Ellogon AI B.V.
summary:
Research in search engine technology, recommender systems and natural language understanding, with a focus to question-answering and conversational search.

Projects on professional search (e.g. legal document retrieval, retrieval for systematic reviews), search personalization, text summarization, information extraction, evaluation (test collections, A/B testing, interleaving).
